OL,3,CGovernment scraps plan to house asylum
OL,4,Cseekers at RAF Scampton
OL,6,FThe government has scrapped plans to
OL,7,Fhouse asylum seekers at RAF Scampton.
OL,9,FThe former airbase, in Lincolnshire,
OL,10,Fwas due to start accommodating
OL,11,Fmigrants from later this year as part
OL,12,Fof proposals by the previous
OL,13,FConservative government to reduce the
OL,14,Freliance on hotels.
OL,16,FBut the Home Office said the plan
OL,17,Fwould have cost #122million by the end
OL,18,Fof its use in 2027, which it said was
OL,19,Fnot value for money.
