OL,6,FBorder security and asylum minister
OL,7,FDame Angela Eagle said: "Faster asylum
OL,8,Fprocessing, increased returns and
OL,9,Ftighter enforcement of immigration
OL,10,Frules will reduce demand for
OL,11,Faccommodation like Scampton and save
OL,12,Fmillions for the taxpayer as we drive
OL,13,Fforward work to clear the asylum
