OL,3,CGovernment scraps plan to house asylum
OL,4,Cseekers at RAF Scampton
OL,6,FScampton was home to the famous
OL,7,FDambusters squadron during the Second
OL,8,FWorld War and later the Red Arrows
OL,9,Faerobatics team.
OL,11,FIn 2018, the Ministry of Defence (MoD)
OL,12,Fannounced the base would shut as part
OL,13,Fof cost-cutting measures. It
OL,14,Feventually shut
OL,16,FIn March 2023 West Lindsey District
OL,17,FCouncil unveiled what it called "a
OL,18,Flandmark deal" to buy the 800-acre
OL,19,Fsite from the MoD and transfer
OL,20,Fownership to its new development
OL,21,Fpartner Scampton Holdings Limited.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
