OL,4,Cseekers at RAF Scampton
OL,6,FThe #300m deal aimed to regenerate the
OL,7,Fsite by providing aviation heritage,
OL,8,Fbusiness, aerospace, space and
OL,9,Faviation technology, and education
OL,10,Fopportunities.
OL,12,FThose plans appeared to be scuppered
OL,13,Fwhen, within days, reports emerged
OL,14,Fthat the Home Office was considering
OL,15,Fusing the site to house hundreds of
OL,16,Fasylum seekers.
OL,18,FIt said alternatives were needed to
OL,19,Fkeeping migrants in hotels, which cost
OL,20,Fit said was costing taxpayers
OL,21,F#60million a day.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
