OL,3,CGovernment scraps plan to house asylum
OL,4,Cseekers at RAF Scampton
OL,6,FBut the news was met with widespread
OL,7,Fanger in the area.
OL,9,FThe immigration minister later
OL,10,Fconfirmed that Scampton would house up
OL,11,Fto 2,000 asylum seekers at any one
OL,12,Ftime, mostly originating from
OL,13,FAfghanistan, Iraq and Iran.
OL,15,FThe first were understood to be
OL,16,Farriving this October.
OL,18,FProtracted legal action followed as
OL,19,Fthe council tried to block the plan,
OL,20,Fbut its attempts failed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
