OL,3,CGovernment scraps plan to house asylum
OL,4,Cseekers at RAF Scampton
OL,6,FThe scrapping of the Scampton plan
OL,7,Fcomes after the government ditched the
OL,8,FRwanda policy championed by the Tories
OL,9,Fin government aimed at deterring
OL,10,Fmigrants crossing the Channel in small
OL,11,Fboats.
OL,13,FPeter Hewitt, chairman of Scampton
OL,14,FHoldings, said: "We are incredibly
OL,15,Fexcited, and relieved, not just for
OL,16,Fourselves but for the people of
OL,17,FScampton and the surrounding areas
OL,18,Fwho've been living in a terrible
OL,19,Fperiod of anxiety and uncertainty,
OL,20,Fwhich I know has affected their lives
OL,21,Fover the last 18 months.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
