OL,6,F"We're also very excited that we're
OL,7,Fhopefully on the path now to
OL,8,Fdelivering that very exciting
OL,9,Fdevelopment project."
OL,11,FWriting on X, Labour's Lincoln MP
OL,12,FHamish Falconer welcomed the end of
OL,13,Fwhat he called the Conservatives'
OL,14,F"disastrous scheme".
OL,16,F"Excellent news for Lincoln and
OL,17,FLincolnshire today," he said.
